data.description: Beautiful townhome in Apple Valley.  Don't miss this updated two bedroom, three bathroom.  Great surroundings, with trails to parks, Cobblestone Lake, fishing peer, and amenities including an in-ground pool, common garden, and outdoor workout area.  Open concept living on the main level.  The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, maple woodwork, Cambria countertops, tile backsplash and a breakfast bar.  Living room features a fireplace and entertainment center.  Dedicated dining area opens up to the main level deck.  The upper level features two bedrooms.  The Primary includes a walk-in closet and en-suite with separate shower and jetted tub.  The lower level hosts the laundry and garage access.  Make this your home today!
